	<h3>About Sunday Contest:</h3>

	The Sunday Contest started in 2004 as a weekly unofficial competition hosted by Tyson Mao, and was later hosted by Jon Morris in 2005. After several years of it being inactive, we decided that it would be cool to bring it back as a full-fledged web app. We took the original idea of Sunday Contest and expanded it to include more official WCA events and a ranking system. Of course, just like the original Sunday Contest, we offer weekly prizes to the participants.

