	<h3>Rules:</h3>
	Each week there will be four events hosted. 3x3 Speedsolve, and three other randomly selected events. </br></br>
	One of these events will be selected to be the "featured event". The winner of the featured event wins a $5.00 gift card code to <a href = "http://SpeedCubeShop.com">SpeedCubeShop.com</a>.</br></br>
	Additionally, each week one participant will be randomly selected to win a $5.00 gift card code to <a href = "http://SpeedCubeShop.com">SpeedCubeShop.com</a>.</br></br>
	Each week, your times must be submitted before Saturday at 11:59 PM PST. A new contest begins every Sunday.</br></br>


	Each event is an average of 12 solves, except for 6x6 and 7x7, which are an average of 5. Each competitior receives the same scrambles.</br></br>

	Filming is encouraged, but not required.</br></br>

	All WCA rules, except those that require a delegate or additional people to be present, apply. You can read up on those rules <a href = "https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/">here.</a></br></br>

	Only one account per person is allowed.

	We reserve the right to hold out prizes if we suspect cheating. 
